message.content:
cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on processing raw visual input and using object-centric prediction formulation based on visual glimpses. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses equipping an agent with an internal model of the dynamics of the external world and using it to plan novel actions. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves training a model through random interaction with different environments. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper discusses planning goal-directed actions in varied, unexpected settings, which is a central requirement of intelligent agents in robotics. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves modeling the dynamics of the external world and using it to plan actions, which is a key aspect of control systems.
